data.description: Nestled in Boise, this charming 3 bed, 2 bath home offers a rare opportunity to live on .88 acres without the restrictions of HOA fees, while still being close to schools, shopping, and all necessities. Featuring a 32 x 40 shop, RV parking, barn/stable, lush pasture, fruit trees, and garden beds ready for planting. This home is ready for its new owner!
